<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der
                            <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die der <expan>Eystett<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                        Niclas <expan>Wechsl<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>güt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die ewr <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> Görg
                                <expan>Aman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vorzeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>kawft</expan> sol <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> für uns besant und mit in
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                        Die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>,
                        daz sie das von ir notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> umb redlich schulde, die in der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Görg, ewr
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan>, schuldig beleib und lange zeit
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> hab. Wie
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit in geredt, daz sie die
                                <expan>obgen<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> zu disem mal ablassen
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>, ir wellet umb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fleiss darczu tun, daz die
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> schulde on vercziehen beczalt und auszgericht
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Thome
                        <expan>App<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
